3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with learning semantic similarity between images. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image retrieval tasks with continuous labels. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper deals with retrieval tasks and proposes a triplet mining strategy.
